author: Allison Carey, The Plain Dealer
title: Free removal of racially influenced tattoos offered by Skin Deep Medi Spa in Strongsville
text: Skin Deep Medi Spa in Strongsville is offering up to four free sessions of laser tattoo removal of any racially influenced tattoos. The offer is for a limited time.
